name: Wayne
bio: If you’re looking for a guy who will sweetly kiss your forehead and hold your hand, I’m not your guy.

name: Betty
bio: I’m a foodie, a beer snob, a dog lover, and a proud nerd. I’m not shallow, but you better know how to keep the conversation going, because I have more to offer than just my body. Feel free to drop me a line.

name: Jason
bio: I have a job, my own place, and I’m a fairly decent cook. I love to laugh and have a good time. I’m looking for someone who can hold a conversation and has a good sense of humor.

name: Kate
bio: Hey! I'm looking to meet someone special. I'm 4'10 so all short kings are welcome:) I love going on hikes and dressing up

name: Francis
bio: RESPECT! If you don't got it, then keep walking. Loving the Seattle life but I need someone to explore it with, let's see where life takes us.

name: Lori
bio: Animal lover! Own two German Shepherds so if you have any pets we’ll get along great.

name: Aaron
bio: What’s up? I’m a super chill guy, looking for a girl who’s down to hang out and have fun. Like concerts, dogs, hip hop, non-fiction, and skiing. Hit me up!
